  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "WashCentral ships with its own training platform, the Academy.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 3.501,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "Click the graduation cap.",
      "startS": 3.738,
      "endS": 5.075,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "You land on My Dashboard, your learning home base.",
      "startS": 5.461,
      "endS": 8.672,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "Notice the top-right corner: search and Ask Shyne follow you in here too.",
      "startS": 9.094,
      "endS": 10.526,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "Same platform, different wing.",
      "startS": 10.741,
      "endS": 15.44,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "Read the sidebar before anything else.",
      "startS": 15.84,
      "endS": 18.183,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "The Academy group holds the four places a learner lives:",
      "startS": 18.915,
      "endS": 22.239,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "your dashboard, the catalog, learning paths, and your own course list.",
      "startS": 22.543,
      "endS": 27.067,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "Below it sits an Admin group.",
      "startS": 27.687,
      "endS": 29.41,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "That is the back office, another lesson entirely, and we stay out of it today.",
      "startS": 29.88,
      "endS": 34.56,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Four tiles across the top.",
      "startS": 34.96,
      "endS": 36.595,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Enrolled, completed, hours, certificates.",
      "startS": 37.013,
      "endS": 38.544,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "Every one reads zero because this account has never taken a course,",
      "startS": 38.811,
      "endS": 40.442,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "and that is worth seeing once:",
      "startS": 40.96,
      "endS": 44.879,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "it is exactly what a brand new client learner sees on day one.",
      "startS": 45.287,
      "endS": 46.992,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "These four numbers are your status at a glance.",
      "startS": 47.244,
      "endS": 53.84,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Under the tiles, Continue Learning.",
      "startS": 54.24,
      "endS": 55.703,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "This is the resume slot.",
      "startS": 55.703,
      "endS": 57.622,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "When you are partway through a course, it surfaces here",
