      "id": "p22",
      "text": "and View All opens the fuller list.",
      "startS": 68.431,
      "endS": 70.48,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Look closer at the card, hands off the buttons.",
