      "text": "twenty two courses in all, none started on this account.",
      "startS": 180.866,
      "endS": 183.882,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "And My Learning keeps your own record across four tabs, every one at zero today.",
      "startS": 184.895,
      "endS": 189.791,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p60",
      "text": "We point without opening.",
      "startS": 190.74,
      "endS": 191.966,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p61",
      "text": "Their interiors are a walk for another lesson.",
      "startS": 192.295,
      "endS": 194.56,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p62",
      "text": "One rule before you explore on your own.",
      "startS": 194.96,
      "endS": 196.952,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p63",
      "text": "Browsing, hovering, reading: all free.",
